---
title: Sesame Teriyaki Beef Meatballs with Tenderstem® Broccoli and Basmati Rice
description: These Sesame Teriyaki Beef Meatballs are a crowd pleaser and one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R09_W22_UK_F13251-4_Main_low-818a13a4.jpg
